🚀 Welcome to NexusOS ZFS Live Environment!

📋 Key Features:
  • Native ZFS root filesystem support with ZFSBootMenu
  • Boot environments for easy system snapshots and rollback
  • AI/ML development environment with PyTorch & TensorFlow
  • Gaming support with Steam, Lutris, and Wine
  • Universal package manager (nexuspkg) supporting multiple formats
  • KDE Plasma desktop environment

🛠️  Quick Commands:
  • nexus-zfs-setup.sh  - Install NexusOS with ZFS root
  • zfs list            - View ZFS datasets
  • zpool status        - Check ZFS pool status
  • nexuspkg install    - Universal package installer

📖 Documentation: https://nexusos.org/docs
💬 Support: https://nexusos.org/support

